quran[62]{c,v,t}:
  53,1,"Mi woo…óndirii hoodere si konde fukkiima"
  53,2,"Gondiijo mon majjaani o bewaani."
  53,3,"O haalata kadi belaa…óe."
  53,4,"Ndee [Alqur‚Äôaanaare] wonaani, si wonaa waajo bahyatee…óo."
  53,5,"Ko joom semmbe janngini …óum mbo."
  53,6,"Joom mbaadi yoo…óndi o fotondiri."
  53,7,"Hombo woni e jookli toow…ói."
  53,8,"refti o …ďadi o …ďattii."
  53,9,"O woni …ďadii…óo fotde lah√Īe …ói…óe wolla ko …ďuri …ďadaade."
  53,10,"O wahyii e maccu…óo makko ko o wahyii ko."
  53,11,"…ďernde mum fennaani e ko o yi'i ko."
  53,12,"mbele ho…óon njeddandira e mum ko yi'i."
  53,13,"Ko noon tigi o yi'i Jibriir laawol go…óngol."
  53,14,"ka lekki jaa…ďi njani sanne(haa…ótirdi)."
  53,15,"ko kiin lekki woni aljanna ko…óir…óo."
  53,16,"Nde muurata e lekki jaa…ďi-he ko naatata."
  53,17,"Gite …óe oon√Īaaki nde njawtaani keerol."
  53,18,"Ko goonga o yi'i e kaawsaaji Alla …ďur…ói he mawnide."
  53,19,"Onon he'efer…ďe mbelr on nji'i laata e ujjaa."
  53,20,"E manaata tata…ďiija go…ó…óo oon ne."
  53,21,"Mbele hina woodani on gorko na woodani Mbo debbo."
  53,22,"…óuum de wadde ko peccugol ngol nuun…óaani."
  53,23,"…ói ngonah si wonah in…óe …óe innu…óon onon e baabiraa…ďe mon Alla jippinaani heen daliil …ďe ndewaani si wona sikke e mbelamme pittaali ko goongo peewal arii e ma…ď…ďe ummaade to Joom mu'en."
  53,24,"wolla mbele na woodani ne…ó…óo ko o woo…óa ko."
  53,25,"Ko Alla woodani ko sakkati e ko adii ko."
  53,26,"Heewii e maleykaaji e ndeer kammuuji …ói tefoore majji nafatah hu'unde tawi wonah caggal de Alla sakkitani wonan'de mbo O wela O."
  53,27,"Pellet …ďeen …ďe ngoon…óinaani La'akara ho…ďe innira maleykaaji in…óe rew…ďe."
  53,28,"Woodanaani …ďe ganndal, alah ko…ďr ndewata si wona sikke, pellet sikke nafatae goonga hay hu'unde."
  53,29,"…óuurno oon nduntii…óa jikru amen mbo yi…óah si wona nguurndam aduna."
  53,30,"Ko …óoon ganndal mum en haa…ói, pellet ko Alla …ďuri anndude oon majju…óo laawol makko, ko KaŇčko kadi …ďuri anndude oon peew…óo."
  53,31,"Ko Alla woodani kala ko woni e kammuuji e leydi ngam o yo…ďa …ďeen bonnu…ďe ko…ďe mbonni ko, o yo…ďa kadi mo∆ī∆īin…ďe mo∆ī∆īoore."
  53,32,"…ďeen wo…ó…óitotoo…ďe bakkatuuji maw…ói …óin e paŇčkare […ďe paggitotaako] si wonaa tokoosi …óin. Pellet, Joomi maa ko jaac…óo yaafuyee. Ko KaŇčko …ďuri anndude on gila O pu…ó…óunoo on ummaade e leydi, e nde ngonno…óon fu∆ī∆īannde ka deedi neeniraa…ďe mon. Wota on mantu ko'e mon; ko KaŇčko …ďuri anndude gooŇč…óu…ďe …ďren."
  53,33,"E a tinaali …óuurnii…óo oon,"
  53,34,"hino okkira see…óaa, hooti o …óawa?"
  53,35,"Kere o jogi ganndal mbirnii…ói ngal o yi'irta?"
  53,36,"Kaa o humpitaaka ko woni kon e …óeri Muusa …óiin"
  53,37,"e [ka …óeri] Ibraahiima kuu…ďnu…óo [ahadi yottini]"
  53,38,"won'de woŇčkii [woo] ronndotaako doŇčgal (bakkaat) wo…ókii goo,"
  53,39,"e won'de alanaa ne…ó…óanke, si wonaa ko o golli kon;"
  53,40,"e won'de golle makko …óeen, aray ka yi'ee,"
  53,41,"Refti o yo…ďire …óe njo…ďdi timmundi,"
  53,42,"e wonan'de ko ka Joomi ma woni haattirde ndeen."
  53,43,"e won'de ko KaŇčko woni beltinoowo gullinoowo"
  53,44,"ko KaŇčko kadi woni barooro Wuurnita,"
  53,45,"e won'de O tagii resindiray…ói …óin …ói…ói : gorel e deyel,"
  53,46,"immorde e to…ď…ďere maniiyu si yuppaama,(e raŇčŇča)."
  53,47,"e wonnode ko KaŇčko woodani tagitugol …óimmum."
  53,48,"e won'de ko KaŇčko woni gal…óin…óo e gokku…óo,"
  53,49,"e won'de ko KaŇčko woni Jey…óo hoodere Si'ira ndeen,"
  53,50,"e won'de ko KaŇčko halki Aadi'en adinoo…ďe,"
  53,51,"e Samuuda'en, o heddaano hay e gooto,"
  53,52,"Ko non kadi yim…ďe Nuuhu …ďeen ko adii[…ďe], pellet, …ďeen laatino …ďur…ďe too√Īude e bewde."
  53,53,"e yim…ďe fitaare …ďeen (…ďe) o waylitunoo:"
  53,54,"O hippiri …óe ko ko o hippiri."
  53,55,"Ko hol…óum e neemaaji Joomi ma …óiin cikkitoto…óaa?"
  53,56,"Oo ko jeertinoowo jiyaa…óo e jeertinoo…ďe adinoo…ďe."
  53,57,"Darngal ngal noon …ďadiima."
  53,58,"Du√Īoowo ngal ko woori Allah, ala."
  53,59,"E ko ndee yeewtere [Alqur'aana] kaaweto…óon?"
  53,60,"Ho…óon njala, on ngullataa?"
  53,61,"Te ko on welsindii…ďe?"
  53,62,"Kooni cujjanee Allah, ndewon [mo]."
